<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٥٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1322">حَجَّاجُ بْنُ مِنْهَالٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4340">عَدِيٌّ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> كَانَ فِي سَفَرٍ، فَقَرَأَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فِي الْعِشَاءِ فِي إِحْدَى الرَّكْعَتَيْنِ بِالتِّينِ وَالزَّيْتُونِ» تَقْوِيمٍ الْخَلْقِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>